        <briefdescription>
<para>Specifies the plugin unloading mode for hipDNN. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This enumeration defines when plugins are unloaded from memory:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>HIPDNN_PLUGIN_UNLOAD_LAZY: Keeps plugins loaded until application exit or when hipdnnSetEnginePluginPaths_ext is called. This avoids expensive plugin reloading when handles are frequently created and destroyed.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>HIPDNN_PLUGIN_UNLOAD_EAGER: Unloads plugins immediately when all handles are released. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
